{{Non-diffusing parent category|ATU 480 The Kind and the Unkind Girls}}
'''ATU 460-499''' represents a range of ATU numbers. The [[Aarne–Thompson–Uther Index]] catalogues specific themes found in folktales. The tales in this category are catalogued using numbers within the broad ''Supernatural Tasks'' range.

